{"id":1698,"date":"2024-08-26T19:29:23","date_gmt":"2024-08-26T19:29:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1698"},"modified":"2024-08-26T19:29:23","modified_gmt":"2024-08-26T19:29:23","slug":"houndoomite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/","title":{"rendered":"Houndoomite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Houndoomite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in the Shadow Base B3F. The stone is hidden in the boxes behind the yellow sofa.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Houndoom<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat Shadow Boss Zeff at the Shadow Base<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to your house at Frozen Heights and head west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-players-house-at-frozen-heights.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly come across a frozen lake. Walk onto the lake and follow it north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-frozen-lake-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the frozen lake north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the frozen lake north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see the Shadow Base entrance you want to go through in the lake\u2019s northwest corner.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-shadow-base.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Shadow Base. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Shadow Base.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head east directly after entering the base.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-going-east.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path going east. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path going east.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go through the broken door and head north to enter the elevator.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/05-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-elevator.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the elevator. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the elevator.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speak with the Team Shadow member and have her take you to the base\u2019s B3F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/06-pokemon-unbound-selecting-the-bases-b3f.jpg\" alt=\"Selecting the base\u2019s B3F. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Selecting the base\u2019s B3F.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Follow the path going west after exiting the elevator.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/07-pokemon-unbound-going-west-after-exiting-the-elevator.jpg\" alt=\"Going west after exiting the elevator. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going west after exiting the elevator.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly reach a room with a yellow sofa. <\/p>\n<p>Interact with the box behind the sofa to get the Houndoomite.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/houndoomite\/08-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-houndoomite-behind-the-yellow-couch.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the Houndoomite behind the yellow couch. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the Houndoomite behind the yellow couch.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1699,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1698","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1698","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1699"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1698"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=